    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Wipe, scrub, brush… And enjoy sparkling clean rooms worthy of a  Royal! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301050/extras/57253f89d39dd6668d3f10ea43c25017.poster.avif?t=1770819953\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301050/extras/57253f89d39dd6668d3f10ea43c25017.webm?t=1770819953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301050/extras/57253f89d39dd6668d3f10ea43c25017.mp4?t=1770819953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A heartwarming love story in a brand new sparkling place! <br>Love is in the air, and so is the scent of squeaky-clean success! Beth and Ross's relationship blooms as they team up to tackle dirt, grime, and any mess that stands in their way – through the power of teamwork... and a shared vision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 100 hidden object levels, new mini-games, and a brand new storyline</strong> - make everything shine like never before!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Point and click - solve hidden object puzzles, and get star rewards!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progress the story by using up your stars - do tasks, talk to people, renovate the Cleaning Queens HQ!</strong></p></li></ul>",
